Add the ability to set a minimum number of reviewers that need to have "completed" a review before the review is moved to 'Ready to Close'.

Currently all reviewers in the review have to have selected 'Complete' before the state will change to Ready to Close.

For context the original customer suggestion;

{quote}
.....a feature request to allow me to set the minimum number of reviewers that need to complete the review before the review is moved to 'Ready to Close'. This way, we can still add everyone in the team and they receive the reminder emails etc. but when the threshold is passed the creator can still easily tell the review is effectively complete and has moved to 'Ready to Close' - even when there are more reviewers linked to the review that have not completed.
{quote}
